---
title: Garlic & Herb Crumbed Fish Fingers with Garden Salad & Wedges
description: Take our word for it – once you've had homemade fish fingers, you'll never look back. Served with oven baked potato wedges and  a garden salad, you’ll be throwing yourself at this dish before it’s even hit the dinner table!
